:2360110,"uid":61543,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A：其實咁樣打燈有CCTV 佢就睇到哂 驚唔驚嫁？ <br />\n（含緊） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：影到你個樣 <br />\n（含） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：唔好流出去喎。你會呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：梗係想啦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：唔好啦。流出去就拍咁短，唔想見樣呀。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：好啦好啦。陣間拍多段。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（奶粒的+含） <br />\n（用手chok緊，背景有呻吟聲） <br />\nA：但你幫我含點可以唔見樣？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：咩呀？（手chok緊j)你想影埋我含咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：梗係啦（A fing左兩下j, 個B又含）實見到樣個喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：我落去啦/唔錄落去啦（呢到聽唔清楚） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：做咩呀？好似巴士咁呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：哈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：好似搭巴士咁呀？（B隻手chok緊）做咩呀？（隔左陣） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA/B（？）： 都影唔到呢度環境 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA/B（？）：真係。影左好似無影到，都唔覺得呢度係課室。哈哈哈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（鏡頭影住個B打飛機，之後含返A） <br />\nA：（呻吟聲）吮死我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（個鏡頭完全影到B個樣） <br />\n（之後B用手捽緊） <br />\nB：爽死你啦（好細聲） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（又含） <br />\nA：（呻吟） <br />\n之後鏡頭轉就無套 <br />\nA：你個窿呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：你再lam(?)實d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（鏡頭又轉，入左） <br />\nA：入左未呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：入左（好細聲） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA開始搖 <br />\nB：唔好啊x2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：痛呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（鏡頭再轉，B狂un） <br />\nA：（呻吟聲） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（un左一輪） <br />\nA：好近（勁）呀！你夾我呀？我feel到你夾我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：（呻吟） <br />\n（鏡頭見到B前後咁毓，之後上下un） <br />\n鏡頭再轉，插到啪啪聲，估計兩個人已全裸 <br />\nA：嗌啦（啪啪啪x n） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB：Hi啦（呻吟） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鏡頭影到兩人狗仔式，A應該全裸，B個件衫去掀到胸上面，下身赤裸 <br />\nA啪緊B，背景有呻吟聲 <br />\n鏡頭又影返B個pat pat</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31c008e286a602afd274e71ab39b39b239887c55","tid":2360110,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"片?"},{"pid":"cd6a08bfeb153224a05b616119576b25a105b1d6","tid":2360110,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53afb11040bdfceaf331a71c7310bbfc0ef560ba","tid":2360110,"uid":61543,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A：其實咁樣打燈有CCTV 佢就睇到哂 驚唔驚嫁？ <br />\n（含緊） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA：影到你個樣 <br />\n（含） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hk